        "tab": "Art Building Filosoffen",
        "paragraphs": [
            "In 2019, during my time in Denmark, I visited Filosoffen, a cozy café and art space located in the heart of Odense. After meeting the kind people who worked there, we agreed to host an exhibition in November. I framed and brought 11 of my works from Ukraine, which were displayed on the second floor of the café, offering a beautiful view of the surroundings. The opening was a pleasant event, with many visitors appreciating my paintings."
